<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
      i18n:domain="launchpad">

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-details" />
</metal:leftportlets>

<metal:rightportlets fill-slot="portlets_two">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-actions" />
</metal:rightportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <h1>Feature Tracking in Launchpad</h1>

  <p class="documentDescription">
    Launchpad includes a feature tracker for applications and distributions.
    Use this to plan your development roadmap.
  </p>

  <p>
    The 10 most recently registered specifications in Launchpad:
  </p>

  <tal:block repeat="spec context/latest_specs">
    <b><span tal:replace="spec/target/title">Spec Target Title</span>:</b>
    <br />
    <div tal:replace="structure spec/@@+listing-detailed" />
  </tal:block>

  <p>
    Features are tracked per distribution, and per product registered in the
    Launchpad. Go to a specific product or distribution to see all the
    planned features for that group, or to register new feature
    specifications.
  </p>


</div>
</body>
</html>
